        is-windows-broken.com is an independent informational service and is not Microsoft, not Windows, and not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or approved by Microsoft Corporation. The information provided here is offered “as is” without warranties of any kind. No responsibility or liability is accepted for update failures, outages, data loss, business interruption, security incidents, or any other direct or indirect damages arising from reliance on this site. Always verify all patching decisions against official Microsoft documentation and your own testing before changing production systems.
      </p>
